name: Elise LastName
description:
Elise is the fifth in a new set of custom LastName characters, for anyone who wants a consistent character for their SD 1.5 renders. (v2 now available!)

Elise is the stunning Icelandic girl you met in Reykjavik during your gap year after college. She's a trainee nurse by day, and an almost-professional ice skater by night. She looks really, really good in a sparkly dress. She looks really, really good in a bikini. Her favorite colors are blue, gray, and blue-gray. It's far too expensive for you to ever move to Reykjavik, but she's far too beautiful for you to not keep in touch anyway.

To use this embedding with the Automatic1111 web UI, save the downloaded file to /embeddings/eliselastnamesd15.pt, and then include the trigger word eliselastnamesd15 in your prompt.

(Inspired by Zovya's Nobody series, which is awesome. Go download all of their amazing characters.)

(All of the sample images have full metadata, and are straight out of the sausage machine - no upscaling, inpainting, or img2img-ing.)

modelVersions.description:
Changes in v2:

  • More photorealistic look overall

  • Has much less of a gray / muting effect on the output than v1

  • Generates more realistic hair

  • Doesn’t cause a stranding or grayness on materials that could sometimes happen with v1

  • Is not quite as young-looking by default
